{"title":"谒一江山烈士纪念塔","authors":["何信峰"],"dates":[{"year":1995,"month":6,"day":9}],"parts":[{"type":"paragraph","text":"谒一江山烈士纪念塔"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"何信峰"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"我默默拾级而上"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"一个寂寞的黄昏"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"山间浮云暗绿"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"树鸟悄然无声"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"瞻仰这光辉的纪念塔"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"怀念那大胡子老班长"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"和高个子的战士……"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"还记得我吗？"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"当年渔岛上的"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"第一代红领巾"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"——听过你们英雄的故事"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"乘过你们威武的舰艇"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"节日与你们一起联欢"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"换防与你们相互通信"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"当出征的军号重新响起"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"你们捷速登占"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"一江山大陈"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"国之边陲海之大门"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"多少年来潮起潮落"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"我耿耿纪念高贵的英灵"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"椒江停住了喧哗"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"海市侧耳聆听"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"枫山上我默默致哀"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"任晚风吹冷我的衣襟"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"生如春花之绚丽"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"死如秋叶之静美"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"灵魂里呼啸"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"伟大的脉搏"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"在海浪中搏动"}],"comments":[],"comment_pivots":[],"description":"","page_start":12,"page_end":12}